info<-country_data%>%
  activate(nodes)%>%
  mutate(betweenness = centrality_betweenness(normalized = TRUE),

         transitivity = transitivity(country_data,type = "local"),

  select(name,betweenness,closeness,transitivity,degree)%>%
  as.data.frame()
